{"name":"Lute of the Acute Brute","permission":{"default":0,"xVCY8TaEyq1Er5RJ":3},"type":"weapon","data":{"containerSpace":1,"description":"<p>When strummed, the sound of this axe-shaped (d8 damage) instrument makes the Strength and Presence score of anyone hearing it swap scores for the next d6 days. Repeated listening has no effect.</p>","carryWeight":1,"equipped":false,"price":0,"quantity":1,"damageDie":"1d8","handed":"1","weaponType":"melee"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/morkborg/tokens/players/sacrilegious_songbird.png","effects":[],"_id":"QyQZJjqwxPUM7xzH"}
{"_id":"Y0KSTCrUAQNoBKEX","name":"Sacrilegious Songbird","permission":{"default":0,"xVCY8TaEyq1Er5RJ":3},"type":"class","data":{"abilities":"<p><span style=\"font-size: 1.5em;\">A deal was struck (d6)</span></p>\n<ol>\n<li>In an outhouse just outside Grift.</li>\n<li>Hiding from guards in Galgenbeck.</li>\n<li>In a W&auml;stland noble&rsquo;s bedchamber.</li>\n<li>Dreaming in a disremembered ditch.</li>\n<li>In a Schleswig prison cell.</li>\n<li>Minutes from freezing to death on the way to Alli&aacute;ns.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Abilities</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Your amplified personality makes up for a soul bartered, roll 3d6+2 for Presence.</li>\n<li>A hard life lived has you set for an early grave, roll 3d6-2 for Toughness.</li>\n<li>Roll d6 on the weapon table and d3 on the armor table.</li>\n<li>You carry an aura of unnatural charm everywhere you go, capable of unsettling foes and calming friends, spend a use of your daily Powers to add or subtract d6 to any Morale check.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Accursed Instrument (d6)</h2>\n<p>When you made your life-and-soul-altering deal, you were gifted one (1) of the following accursed instruments:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Gutpipes of Destiny</li>\n<li>Hurty-Gurdy</li>\n<li>Spinal Husk</li>\n<li>The Devil's Aquifer</li>\n<li>Mouth-to-Mouth-Organ</li>\n<li>Lute of the Acute Brute</li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>","armorTableDie":"1d3","description":"Always the bringer of unwelcome sounds, your vocation as a bard left you destitute and disreputable... until the rueful day when a being of impious character made you the deal of a lifetime. Your soul may be screaming, but your throat sings sweetly, and your purse ever sweeter. A small price to pay.","omenDie":"1d2","startingAgility":"3d6","startingHitPoints":"1d6","startingItems":"morkborg.class-sacrilegious-songbird,Unnatural Charm","startingPresence":"3d6+2","startingRolls":"morkborg.rolls-sacrilegious-songbird,A deal was struck,1\nmorkborg.rolls-sacrilegious-songbird,Accursed Instruments,1","startingSilver":"4d6*10","startingStrength":"3d6","startingToughness":"3d6-2","weaponTableDie":"1d6"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/morkborg/tokens/players/sacrilegious_songbird.png","effects":[]}
{"name":"Spinal Husk","permission":{"default":0,"xVCY8TaEyq1Er5RJ":3},"type":"shield","data":{"containerSpace":1,"description":"<p>When beating this drum made from a hellion&rsquo;s shell, roll 2d6:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>6+ - Everyone except you tests Agility against DR14 or falls prone.</li>\n<li>11 - Choose d4 creatures that can hear your drumming. Their spines break like twigs. You cannot use the drum again today.</li>\n<li>12 - Your ears won&rsquo;t stop ringing; you are deaf for the next 24 hours.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Also doubles as a shield.</p>","carryWeight":1,"equipped":false,"price":0,"quantity":1},"flags":{},"img":"systems/morkborg/tokens/players/sacrilegious_songbird.png","effects":[],"_id":"pXyY69sSXkfrWjan"}
{"name":"Mouth-to-Mouth-Organ","permission":{"default":0,"xVCY8TaEyq1Er5RJ":3},"type":"misc","data":{"containerSpace":1,"description":"<p>Play this bony mouth harp to make a broken listener instantly recover d4 HP. They cannot speak until their HP is fully recovered.</p>","carryWeight":1,"equipped":false,"price":0,"quantity":1},"flags":{},"img":"systems/morkborg/tokens/players/sacrilegious_songbird.png","effects":[],"_id":"trsV86WJ6L8dNw3J"}
{"name":"The Devil's Aquifer","permission":{"default":0,"xVCY8TaEyq1Er5RJ":3},"type":"misc","data":{"containerSpace":1,"description":"<p>The horn of a beelzebubonic creature from the deepest depths of the Endless Sea. When blown, the lungs of your enemies fill with seawater, should they fail a Toughness test against DR14; a round must be spent expelling it before doing anything else.</p>","carryWeight":1,"equipped":false,"price":0,"quantity":1},"flags":{},"img":"systems/morkborg/tokens/players/sacrilegious_songbird.png","effects":[],"_id":"yForLP9hxNVeeY7r"}
